{"tid":1040352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵扶手梯意外 疑乘客大衣勾起鐵片","createTime":"2019-02-28T04:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T06:49:09.000Z","uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75367d694fc60d558ed622b3ea6509a36224eae1","tid":1040352,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"港鐵觀塘線牛頭角站早上發生扶手電梯意外，9人受傷。港鐵事務營運總管鄭群興指出，涉事扶手電梯右側旁板有一支固定旁板部件伸出，觸及扶手電梯上乘客的腳部。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，電梯保養承辦商通力昨日收車後有進行正常維修工作，但承認無檢查涉事部件，而職員早上開站前檢查運作正常，無部件突出，目前正向承辦商了解。<br />\n<br />\n據初步調查發現，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑有乘客穿大衣落扶手電梯時勾起鐵片</span></strong>，隨後的乘客被突出的鐵片弄傷。"},{"pid":"709276755d3cad3eed8527a0bbf8d93fc67b97d0","tid":1040352,"uid":54787,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"勾爛人地件衫仲話人地勾起鐵片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfd035ae83a2dacb6ef9cae02d85b9fc76ae099","tid":1040352,"uid":135158,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"講撚到人地特登著件大衣嚟勾你個濕鳩電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116b89381a9e6240b31931b47650fa813c3f64d4","tid":1040352,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"709276755d3cad3eed8527a0bbf8d93fc67b97d0","tid":1040352,"uid":54787,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"勾爛人地件衫仲話人地勾起鐵片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"喂，你塊面撞落我隻手度呀"},{"pid":"2f08010dd206383e342cabea29d43e344c6d9b16","tid":1040352,"uid":39576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"要地鐵真心認錯難d定減價難d?"},{"pid":"d9c4ba1434b64c7cf68f917814c55ed8b040d799","tid":1040352,"uid":62247,